LICENCE ENFORCEMENT
================================================================================

This software requires a valid licence key issued by VEKTOR Memory via
Polar (polar.sh). Licence keys are validated at runtime and cached locally.
Each key may be activated on up to 3 machines. VEKTOR Memory reserves the
right to revoke any licence key at any time for violation of these terms.

